## 4. How to Combine Market Information

### 4.1 Current State

ALL market data is mock/simulated:
- `server/src/routes/market.js` has 20 hardcoded stocks with random price generation
- `server/src/routes/portfolio.js` uses `simulateCurrentPrice()` with random variation
- News articles are hardcoded with fake timestamps
- No real API calls to any market data provider

### 4.2 Target Architecture

```
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│              EXTERNAL DATA SOURCES               │
│  Polygon.io  |  Alpha Vantage  |  NewsAPI        │
└──────────────────┬───────────────────────────────┘
                   │
                   ▼
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│           MARKET DATA SERVICE (server)           │
│  - Fetch real quotes (cache 60s)                 │
│  - Fetch real news                               │
│  - Calculate technical indicators                │
└──────────────────┬───────────────────────────────┘
                   │
                   ▼
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│           CONTEXT BUILDER                        │
│  Combine:                                        │
│  - Real market data (prices, trends, news)       │
│  - User holdings & watchlist                     │
│  - User profile (risk, goals, knowledge level)   │
│  - User budget & savings data                    │
└──────────────────┬───────────────────────────────┘
                   │
                   ▼
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│           AI ENGINE (Claude API)                 │
│  System prompt + real data context               │
